 <summary>Sample transfer application</summary>
 <description>
  <p>Elektroid is an sample transfer application for Elektron devices.</p>
  <p>With elektroid you can easily load audio files like flac or wav into your
  elektron sampler. You can also transfer audio samples from your elektroid
  device to your local hard disk.</p>
